object attributes</emphasis> in the &PN_MessageQueue; software), see the <citetitle><olink
targetdoc="SJSMQAG"><citetitle remap="book">Sun Java System Message Queue 3 2005Q4
Administration Guide</citetitle></olink></citetitle>.</para></sect3>
