<row rowsep="1">
<entry>
<para><indexterm>
<primary>availability-enabled attribute</primary>
<secondary>availability-service element</secondary>
</indexterm><literal>availability-<?SolBook preflinebreak>enabled</literal></para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para><literal>true</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
<para>(optional) If set to <literal>true</literal>, high-availability features apply
