<row rowsep="1">
<entry>
<para><olink targetptr="abhcg">ejb-timer-service</olink></para></entry>
<entry>
<para>zero or one</para></entry>
<entry>
<para>Configures the EJB timer service.</para></entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<para><olink targetptr="abhed">property</olink></para></entry>
<entry>
