</row>]]><![ %Enterprise; []]><![ %Enterprise; []]>
<row>
<entry>
<para><indexterm>
<primary>acceptor-threads attribute</primary>
</indexterm> <literal>acceptor-threads</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
<para><literal>1</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
<para>(optional) Specifies the number of processors in the machine. <![ %Platform; [The
only legal value is <literal>1</literal>.]]> <remark role="reviewer">For Platform
Edition, the only legal value is 1.</remark></para>
<para>To set the number of request processing threads, use the <literal>thread-count
</literal> attribute of the <olink targetptr="abheh">request-processing</olink> element.
</para></entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<para><indexterm>
<primary>security-enabled attribute</primary>
</indexterm> <literal>security-enabled</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
<para><literal>false</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
