or off and set ciphers, use an <literal>ssl</literal> subelement.</para></entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<para><indexterm>
<primary>default-virtual-server attribute</primary>
</indexterm> <literal>default-virtual<?SolBook preflinebreak>-server</literal></para>
</entry>
<entry>
<para>none</para></entry>
<entry>
