<primary>xpowered-by attribute</primary>
</indexterm><literal>xpowered-by</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
<para><literal>true</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
<para>(optional) If true, <literal>X-Powered-By</literal> headers are used according
to the Servlet 2.4 and JSP 2.0 specifications.</para></entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<para><literal>enabled</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
<para><literal>true</literal></para></entry>
<entry>
