</sect1>
<sect1 id="abhfd"><title>U</title>
<sect2 id="abhfe"><title>user-group</title>
<indexterm>
<primary>user-group element</primary>
</indexterm>
<para>Contains the group to which the principal belongs.</para>
<sect3><title>Superelements</title>
<para><olink targetptr="abhen">security-map</olink></para></sect3>
